---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Product Safety | Lucy Epoxy Studio" 
  description="Product safety and compliance with EU Regulation 2023/988." 
  lang="en" 
  pathname="/en/product-safety"
>
  <Header ctaHref="/en/contact" ctaLabel="Get a quote" />

  <main class="section-sm">
    <div class="container card" style="padding:1.5rem; line-height:1.7;">

      <h1>Product Safety (EU 2023/988)</h1>

      <p>
        In accordance with Regulation (EU) 2023/988 on general product safety,
        we ensure that all products are safe for users.
      </p>

      <h2>Manufacturer Identification</h2>
      <p>
        Lucy Epoxy Studio<br>
        [Your full address]<br>
        Email: contact@yourdomain.com
      </p>

      <h2>Our Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>use of safe and verified materials</li>
        <li>quality control at every stage of production</li>
        <li>providing information on proper use of products</li>
        <li>continuous improvement of safety standards</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Safety and Usage Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>products are made of wood and epoxy resin – avoid high temperatures</li>
        <li>do not place hot items directly on the surface</li>
        <li>avoid strong chemicals and abrasive cleaning agents</li>
        <li>intended for indoor use unless stated otherwise</li>
        <li>handmade product – natural variations may occur</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Product Identification (Traceability)</h2>
      <p>Each product can be identified by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>order number or project name</li>
        <li>date of production</li>
        <li>materials used</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Detailed information is available upon request.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For product safety inquiries, please contact us via the contact form.
      </p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</MainLayout>